text: The VinFast VF 9 is a electric full-size Crossover SUV made by VinFast since 2022. == History and Features == The VinFast VF 9 debuted for the first time in January 2021, being shown alongside the VinFast VF 6 and the VinFast VF 8, with the VF 9 being the largest of the range of electrics crossovers that is the first from this type from VinFast. The VF 9 was then presented in Vietnam in September 2021, with deliveries of the first units starting in 2022. it has two electric motors with 300 kW (402 hp) and a range of 482 km 300 mi). == Markets == The VinFast VF 9 was first launched in the Vietnamese market and is also sold in United States, Canada, Europe, Australia and Philipines. == References == Category:Sport utility vehicles Category:2020s automobiles
